{"tid":919140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"17歲女孩全身8成燒傷　父20次割皮救女：全身的皮都可以給她","createTime":"2018-11-27T22:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T08:16:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":553,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"b446202450c3e7cfc633521c4de30e966701a1b3","tid":919140,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T22:08:48.000Z","msg":"中國河南省新鄉市轄下的高北村1處民宅，10月3日發生1起液化瓦斯爆炸事件，該戶1名17歲李姓少女，全身大面積燒傷送醫急救，父親也入院割皮救女。<br />\n根據《網易》網站報導，這戶李姓人家，當天因廚房的液化瓦斯洩漏，引起爆炸，當時在廚房的李姓少女，穿著短袖短褲全都燒光，「全身都是白皮，跟1張塑膠布一樣」，緊急送醫後發現全身大面積燒傷近八成，一直住在加護病房治療。<br />\n報導中說，就讀高三的李姓少女，品學兼優又十分懂事，是父母的心頭寶貝，受傷之後，父親就入院割皮救女，他說，「全身的皮都可以給她」，想讓女兒早點好起來，目前左腿大小腿，皮膚全都割了給女兒植皮，只能在病床上養傷，無法出去賺錢。<br />\n李姓少女的母親說，家裡是農家，而丈夫除了農作就是打零工，收入不豐，而從事件發生至今約2個月，醫藥費就已經花了120多萬了（約台幣534萬元），除了微薄的積蓄，向親友借貸也已經「借到不能再借了」，鄉里也都捐款了，希望各謝善心人士幫助他們，度過這個難關。<br />\n報導中說，醫院方面表示，李姓少女已經手術了10多次，但目前還沒脫離危險期，因為還需要植皮、封閉全部傷口，而未來面對後遺症與功能障礙，還要進行復健治療，還有許多醫藥費要支付。<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181128/640_cb5065a5f7599c7f3b07a971852410f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181128%2F640_cb5065a5f7599c7f3b07a971852410f8.jpg&h=7fd9bda5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181128/640_4c534a99da6dbf96609f493295637f64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181128%2F640_4c534a99da6dbf96609f493295637f64.jpg&h=2302f410&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181128/640_e5b13a565735fb74c165d302e124e430.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181128%2F640_e5b13a565735fb74c165d302e124e430.jpg&h=126f7481&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181128/1474429/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181128%2F1474429%2F&d=XvVZL%2BGN6co3a6t8aNcdLcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=61d9304b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181128%2F1474429%2F&h=bffd6878\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181128/1474429/</a>"},{"pid":"816e37552bb665e439e4eb95bb2b5580eb2a3288","tid":919140,"uid":72046,"like":336,"dislike":7,"score":329,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T22:13:40.000Z","msg":"慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee63e6175fe617b62e4fe3b5116538cda13baeb","tid":919140,"uid":42188,"like":30,"dislike":476,"score":-446,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T22:13:53.000Z","msg":"包皮都得？"},{"pid":"b7650d53a66ee105e77f176f56ad4d711fc6ed9a","tid":919140,"uid":78304,"like":9,"dislike":71,"score":-62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T22:17:21.000Z","msg":"boom<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c9e17591d76184714642b90f6d2a10dc171daa","tid":919140,"uid":208722,"like":109,"dislike":2,"score":107,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T22:17:21.000Z","msg":"諗起呢個故仔<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FswW2T56Msk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFswW2T56Msk&d=XvVZL%2BGN6co3a6t8aNcdLcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=2191da95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FswW2T56Msk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00c11e0c60c2fa27031f1017ce53f052ee91a0c","tid":919140,"uid":40470,"like":17,"dislike":131,"score":-114,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T23:31:50.000Z","msg":"女仔幾可愛...ok今次算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e8946522bde8586310d4c4f904e48e91d7c114","tid":919140,"uid":53105,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T23:35:37.000Z","msg":"液化瓦斯即係石油氣<img src=\"/ass